                        <div class = "col-sm-6 col-sm-pull-6 main-info">
                            <p>
                                I arrived back in Fresno with enough time to get through security at the airport and make it to my gate on time. I had a quick bite to eat somewhere in the airport but the name of the place escapes me. What I ordered was nothing special, just your average turkey club sandwich and a coke in case you were wondering. My only regret from my trip was not being able to get a rental car for my mini vacation. I was not old enough at the time. Constantly looking at shuttle times was a little stressful but it would have been much easier if I had my own car. If you are old enough to obtain a rental car, I highly suggest you do.
